{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "唐缺因未被邀请参加宴席而心生不满，对无忌态度冷淡。无忌画完肖像后去找上官刃，得知唐家堡有为核心成员画肖像的规矩，意味着假身份已被接受。唐傲亲自接见无忌，带他参观精英肖像画廊，并请画师朱子丹用宣纸透描法画出无忌发胖后的脸型。画出的面容与大风堂赵无忌的画像高度吻合，唐傲借此揭露无忌的真实身份。无忌试图辩解但无法反驳。唐傲展现光明磊落的风范，公开约战七月初七午时于泰山顶上决斗，并透露唐家堡即将对大风堂发动大攻击，让无忌离开回去备战。无忌虽身陷险境，却对唐傲的为人产生敬意。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_que",
      "speaker_name": "唐缺",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你就画好了，唐家堡不喜欢人东问西问的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "上官刃",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "恭喜你！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "text": "恭喜我，为什么？唐家堡难道要拿我的肖像去相亲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "上官刃",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "那当然不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "text": "不然，喜从何来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "上官刃",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐家堡一直有个习惯，他们会替上上下下的主要份子画一张肖像，摆在一间房里，让大家都看得见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "text": "哦？上官大叔也画过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "上官刃",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，这表示他们已经相信你的假身份，并且要重用你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李玉堂？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "不错，绩溪李玉堂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "欢迎你到唐家堡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这是我的荣幸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们到里面再谈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "里面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "是的，里面的房间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去请朱先生到里面的房间来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这些都是我们唐家堡的精英分子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你的肖像在桌上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "朱先生的手上功夫不错吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "一流。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们唐家的规矩，只要是精英分子，我们都会替他画幅肖像，摆放在这房里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不过，这次我们替你画像的原因，却不一定挂在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这是我们唐家堡替人画肖像以来的第一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这应该也是我的荣幸吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "也许，你想知道为什么吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你会告诉我吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "当然会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这五张肖像画的都是唐缺，最左一张大概是十年前，那时他很瘦，最右一张是一年前，他已经胖成这个样子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这张宣纸是经过打簿的，可以把底下的画像透上来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "朱先生擅长人物画，所以对人的观察非常细微，他现在根据他的经验，把你发胖后的脸型画出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "像吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我怎么会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你怎么会不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我从小就是这么瘦，我怎么会知道长胖了会怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "真的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你看我像是这么俊俏的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我看很像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你跟我来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这房里的柜子，放的也是肖像，不同的是，放的都是与我们唐家堡为敌的人的肖像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这是大风堂赵无忌的画像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zi_dan",
      "speaker_name": "朱子丹",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "一模一样，你就是赵无忌！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你还笑得出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你不觉得很好笑吗？你不觉得这是很荒唐的事吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我不觉得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "大风堂的赵无忌画像，是不是他画的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "所以嘛，你们认定我就是赵无忌，所以他加画的时候，很容易就会朝赵无忌的相貌去想，画出来的，当然会是赵无忌，假如你们认为我是飞凤帮的胡敦，我相信他画出来的，一定是胡敦的样子，你信不信？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我信，不过有一点你错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "朱先生事先并不知道赵无忌的事，我们只告诉他你是李玉堂，然后要他根据他的经验，画出李玉堂发胖后的样貌而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你现在承认你就是赵无忌了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你既然早就这么认定，你为什么不早出手杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "有两个原因，第一，你一进来，我就感觉到你蓄势待发的杀气，我不敢保证我一出手就可以击败你，就算击败你，我如果不能全身而退，这种两败俱伤的事，我唐傲是绝对不做的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "哦？那第二个原因呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "第二个原因才是真正的原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我从不做偷袭的事，要杀一个人，我一定堂堂正正的和他决斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "那你准备跟我决斗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你那么肯定我就是赵无忌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不管你是不是赵无忌，我都要和你决斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "与天下英雄论剑，是我唐傲毕生的愿望。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我配吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你当然配，光凭你的胆色就够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你太抬举我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你接受我的挑战吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我能拒绝吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "好，我们一言为定，七月初七午时，泰山顶上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "好，一言为定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "既然我们约好了，我就要请你保重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你这句话我不太懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "为什么不懂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你为什么要我保重？如果没有特殊事故，谁不会保重自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你说得不错，我就是因为知道将会有特殊情况发生，才叫你保重的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "什么特殊事故？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "这几件事，是接二连三发生的，第一件，今天晚上我会让你见一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "见一个人？我一定要见吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "是我答应了别人让你见那个人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "假如我不见呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "那也没关系，是我失信于别人而已，不过，那个人我相信你是一定想见的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "好，我见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "谢谢，第二件事，你见完那个人之后，你就要离开唐家堡，一个人离开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你的意思是，唐家堡已经不欢迎我了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不，我们很欢迎你来作客，我是怕你一刻也不愿意停留。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为我还要告诉你一件事，这件事你听了以后，你一定会急得像热锅上的蚂蚁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "再急也没用，我已经答应你晚上要见一个人，见完以后我才能走，而且是一个人走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你很聪明，能和你一决胜负真是人生一大乐事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "现在一切都在你掌握之中，我可不乐。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "所以我才要把一切都弄得很公平，这样才能正式见个真章。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我们近日就要对大风堂展开大攻击，你会不急着回去吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你为什么还不下手杀上官刃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "唐家堡在江湖上屹立至今，你以为是玩假的吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "好，我告诉你，我还没有找到下手的机会，你相信吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我当然相信，上官刃是什么人物，岂能轻易让你找到机会？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "不过我要先告诉你，我会不断的找机会来报仇的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "我希望你还是先用点心在马上面临的大战上，我不希望攻打大风堂有如切豆腐一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "任何事情如果太容易，就不好玩了，太容易的事，只表示你没有判断力，用一把牛刀去杀鸡，岂非是最愚蠢不过的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这就是你放我回去的原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你那么有必胜的把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "谋定而后动，动必奏功，这是我唐某人的做事原则。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "很好，我喜欢你这样的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "可惜我们不能成为朋友。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "世间事通常都不能尽如人意，能够做面对面的敌人，也已经不错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，有些人连想成为敌人都不可能呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我会永远怀念你这位敌人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "这表示我跟你一样，也具有必胜的信心，打败了你，我就只剩下对你的怀念而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "说得好，你现在愿意跟我去一个地方吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "去什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "本来我是晚上才带你去的，不过，我忽然改变主意，希望你现在就去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你要我现在就去见你说的一个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不，还是晚上再见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "那为什么现在就去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "因为我要你在那里等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "你这是变相的囚禁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "你不敢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "我为什么不敢？不过我想知道，你怕我在这段时间里做出什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_ao",
      "speaker_name": "唐傲",
      "listener": "char_wu_ji",
      "text": "不错，我怕你万一发现了杀上官刃的机会，那可是我们唐家堡的大损失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "无忌",
      "listener": "char_tang_ao",
      "text": "那我们现在就走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    }
  ],
